            <p>This Agreement takes effect when you begin participating in Code for Good events and activities and remains in effect for so long as you continue participating (the “Term”). However, sections 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, and 11 of this Agreement will survive in perpetuity, regardless of termination.</p>
